  <!-- Footer -->
  
<footer class="row">
	<div class="nine columns">
	  <p>&copy; Copyright 2012 <a href="http://nicksantos.com" target="_blank">Nick Santos</a>. Vote Climate Change is a joint project with <a href="http://rooseveltpipeline.org" target="_blank">Roosevelt Institute: Pipeline</a>.<br/>
		  Background image: <a href="http://www.nasa.gov/multimedia/imagegallery/image_feature_2377.html" target="_blank">NASA/GSFC/Jeff Schmaltz/MODIS Land Rapid Response Team</a></p>
	</div>
	<div class="three columns">
	  <ul class="link-list right">
		<li><a href="#">Section 1</a></li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
</footer>


<div id="action_box">
	<p style="font-weight:bold;">Your pledge has been saved and, if your candidate has a twitter handle, sent to the candidate.
	Thanks for pledging!</p>

	<h3>Want to take more action?</h3>
	<p>You can make your pledge even stronger by getting involved with <a href="350.org" target="_blank" class="offsite">350.org</a> or <a href="http://energyaction.org" target="_blank" class="offsite">Energy Action Coalition</a> &mdash; organizations
	working toward making sure the United States addresses climate change and greenhouse gas emissions instead
	of continuing to ignore our future.</p>
	<p>If you want to get involved in your daily life, you can head on over to <a href="http://enviroconsumer.org">Environmental Consumer</a>,
	 which helps you to make smart decisions for yourself and our environment.
	</p>
</div>
<div id="unimplemented_msg">
	<p stlye="font-weight: bold;">This feature is unimplmented. Expect it soon. Thanks for testing!</p>
</div>


